msgstr "Alihkan status mana yang muncul dalam log."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "OK"
msgstr "OK"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Redirect"
msgstr "Pengalihan"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "URL"
msgstr "URL"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Checked at"
msgstr "Diperiksa pada"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Edit post"
msgstr "Sunting pos"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "View post"
msgstr "Lihat postingan"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Open link"
msgstr "Buka tautan"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "pts"
msgstr "poin"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Your SEO title should be long enough to explain the topic, but short enough to avoid truncation."
msgstr "Judul SEO Anda harus cukup panjang untuk menjelaskan topik, tetapi cukup pendek untuk menghindari pemotongan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Aim for about 50–60 characters. Front-load the most important words."
msgstr "Usahakan sekitar 50–60 karakter. Letakkan kata-kata yang paling penting di bagian depan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear, visible titles improve click-through rate from search results."
msgstr "Judul yang jelas dan terlihat meningkatkan rasio klik-tayang dari hasil pencarian."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Search engines expect the primary topic to appear in the title."
msgstr "Mesin pencari mengharapkan topik utama muncul dalam judul."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Include your focus keyphrase naturally near the start of the title."
msgstr "Sertakan frasa kunci fokus Anda secara alami di dekat awal judul."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves topical relevance and makes the result more recognizable."
msgstr "Meningkatkan relevansi topik dan membuat hasil lebih mudah dikenali."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "A meta description helps search engines and users understand the page."
msgstr "Deskripsi meta membantu mesin pencari dan pengguna memahami halaman."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Write 1–2 sentences that summarize the page and invite a click."
msgstr "Tulis 1–2 kalimat yang merangkum halaman dan mengundang klik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Better snippets can lift click-through rate even if rankings stay the same."
msgstr "Snippet yang lebih baik dapat meningkatkan rasio klik-tayang meskipun peringkat tetap sama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Descriptions that are too short or too long get cut off in results."
msgstr "Deskripsi yang terlalu pendek atau terlalu panjang akan terpotong di hasil."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep it roughly 140–160 characters and prioritize the main benefit."
msgstr "Pertahankan sekitar 140–160 karakter dan prioritaskan manfaat utamanya."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Full snippets look more professional and improve engagement."
msgstr "Cuplikan lengkap terlihat lebih profesional dan meningkatkan keterlibatan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the focus phrase helps confirm the page topic."
msgstr "Menyertakan frasa fokus membantu menegaskan topik halaman."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Work the focus keyphrase into the first sentence naturally."
msgstr "Masukkan frasa kunci utama ke dalam kalimat pertama secara alami."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger relevance signals can improve ranking and user confidence."
msgstr "Sinyal relevansi yang lebih kuat dapat meningkatkan peringkat dan kepercayaan pengguna."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Title and description should not repeat each other."
msgstr "Judul dan deskripsi tidak boleh mengulang satu sama lain."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the title to state the topic and the description to add benefit or context."
msgstr "Gunakan judul untuk menyatakan topik dan deskripsi untuk menambahkan manfaat atau konteks."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Distinct messaging gives users more reasons to click."
msgstr "Pesan yang berbeda memberikan lebih banyak alasan bagi pengguna untuk mengklik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Pages should have a single main heading (H1)."
msgstr "Halaman harus memiliki satu heading utama (H1)."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep one H1 that matches the page topic, and use H2/H3 for sections."
msgstr "Pertahankan satu H1 yang sesuai dengan topik halaman, dan gunakan H2/H3 untuk bagian."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear structure helps search engines understand the content hierarchy."
msgstr "Struktur yang jelas membantu mesin pencari memahami hierarki konten."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Subheadings break long content into scannable sections."
msgstr "Subheading memecah konten panjang menjadi seksi yang mudah dipindai."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add 2–8 H2/H3 headings that summarize key sections."
msgstr "Tambahkan 2–8 heading H2/H3 yang merangkum bagian-bagian utama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves readability and keeps users engaged longer."
msgstr "Meningkatkan keterbacaan dan membuat pengguna tetap terlibat lebih lama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in a subheading reinforces the main topic."
msgstr "Menyertakan frasa kunci dalam subjudul memperkuat topik utama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Place the focus keyphrase in one relevant H2 or H3."
msgstr "Tempatkan frasa kunci utama di salah satu H2 atau H3 yang relevan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps search engines connect sections to the main theme."
msgstr "Membantu mesin telusur menghubungkan bagian-bagian ke tema utama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "The opening paragraph sets context for both users and search engines."
msgstr "Paragraf pembuka menetapkan konteks bagi pengguna dan mesin pencari."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus keyphrase once in the first 1–2 sentences."
msgstr "Gunakan frasa kunci utama sekali dalam 1–2 kalimat pertama."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger topical clarity can improve relevance signals."
msgstr "Kejelasan topikal yang lebih kuat dapat meningkatkan sinyal relevansi."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keyphrase density shows how often the main topic appears."
msgstr "Kepadatan frasa kunci menunjukkan seberapa sering topik utama muncul."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the keyphrase naturally throughout the content without stuffing."
msgstr "Gunakan frasa kunci secara alami di seluruh konten tanpa keyword stuffing."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Balanced usage supports relevance while avoiding spam signals."
msgstr "Penggunaan yang seimbang mendukung relevansi sambil menghindari sinyal spam."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long-tail phrases capture more specific search intent."
msgstr "Frasa long-tail menangkap niat pencarian yang lebih spesifik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add your long-tail phrases where they fit naturally in sections."
msgstr "Tambahkan frasa long-tail Anda di bagian yang paling alami."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps the page rank for more specific queries."
msgstr "Membantu halaman mendapat peringkat untuk kueri yang lebih spesifik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Very short pages often lack depth to satisfy readers."
msgstr "Halaman yang sangat pendek sering kali kurang mendalam untuk memuaskan pembaca."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Expand the content with examples, steps, or FAQs."
msgstr "Perluas konten dengan contoh, langkah, atau FAQ."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "More complete content tends to perform better for informational queries."
msgstr "Konten yang lebih lengkap cenderung berkinerja lebih baik untuk kueri informasional."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Readable content keeps users engaged and reduces bounce."
msgstr "Konten yang mudah dibaca membuat pengguna tetap terlibat dan mengurangi pentalan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Shorten sentences, use simpler words, and break up long paragraphs."
msgstr "Persingkat kalimat, gunakan kata yang lebih sederhana, dan pecah paragraf panjang."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improved clarity boosts dwell time and user satisfaction."
msgstr "Kejelasan yang lebih baik meningkatkan dwell time dan kepuasan pengguna."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long sentences are hard to read in CJK languages."
msgstr "Kalimat panjang sulit dibaca dalam bahasa CJK."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Split long sentences and add punctuation for clearer flow."
msgstr "Pecah kalimat panjang dan tambahkan tanda baca untuk alur yang lebih jelas."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clearer reading experience helps users stay on the page."
msgstr "Pengalaman membaca yang lebih jelas membantu pengguna tetap berada di halaman."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Images support understanding and break up long text."
msgstr "Gambar membantu pemahaman dan memecah teks yang panjang."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one relevant image that illustrates the topic."
msgstr "Tambahkan setidaknya satu gambar relevan yang menggambarkan topik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Visuals improve engagement and can help with image search."
msgstr "Visual meningkatkan keterlibatan dan dapat membantu penelusuran gambar."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Alt text helps search engines and screen readers interpret images."
msgstr "Alt text membantu mesin pencari dan pembaca layar menafsirkan gambar."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Describe each image in plain language, focusing on what it shows."
msgstr "Jelaskan setiap gambar dengan bahasa yang sederhana, dengan fokus pada apa yang ditampilkannya."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves accessibility and adds extra relevance signals."
msgstr "Meningkatkan aksesibilitas dan menambahkan sinyal relevansi tambahan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spacing long-tail phrases prevents keyword stuffing."
msgstr "Memberi jarak pada frasa ekor panjang mencegah keyword stuffing."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spread similar phrases across different sections."
msgstr "Sebarkah frasa serupa di berbagai seksi."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keeps content natural while still covering long-tail queries."
msgstr "Menjaga konten tetap alami sambil tetap mencakup kueri long-tail."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in one image alt text reinforces the topic."
msgstr "Menyertakan frasa kunci dalam satu teks alt gambar memperkuat topik."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus phrase in a single relevant image alt description."
msgstr "Gunakan frasa kunci utama dalam satu deskripsi alt gambar yang relevan."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Adds topical relevance without over-optimizing every image."
msgstr "Menambah relevansi topik tanpa mengoptimalkan berlebihan setiap gambar."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Internal links help users and search engines discover related pages."
msgstr "Tautan internal membantu pengguna dan mesin pencari menemukan halaman terkait."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
